# CODEOWNERS
# This file defines who is automatically requested for review
# when a pull request touches specific paths in this repo.
#
# Syntax: <path-pattern>  <owner(s)>
# Rules are matched top to bottom; the LAST matching rule wins,
# so keep general/default rules at the top and more specific
# overrides further down.
#
# Docs: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

